{
  "stem": "21527.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were not terribly observant, but I think they felt very strongly being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had extended family in Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And although there were just the three of us living in Warsaw, there were visits to and from Warsaw that was my family on my father's side.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother had an older brother who lived in a town called Vilna.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother's father, my grandfather, also lived there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My uncle had one son.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was a prominent member of the Vilna Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And every year, we spent about four or five weeks just outside Vilna as a family unit, holidaying.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's quite significant, because we were there on the 1st of September, the day the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we-- I remember hearing it on the radio, an emergency announcement and my mother packing very quickly.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was only five years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I couldn't quite grasp the severity, the, the importance of the announcement.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But after that, we, we must have gone by train from Vilna back to Warsaw, because my father wasn't with us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we-- my father then came back from his holiday where he was into Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was the-- German was already-- Germany was already occupying Warsaw, so we, we made arrangements to leave Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't really remember very, very much, whether there was-- I'm sure there was great anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't remember because as I say, I hadn't even started kindergarten.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was probably in a very sort of very small circle of-- I had some girl little friends because I remember dressing up and going to parties.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were probably all Jewish, so I don't remember being exposed to the outside world.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I said, going-- being-- dressing up.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
